	<section class="features">
        <div class="container faq">
			<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>What is a turtle shelter vest?</h3>
                    <p>A high tech but simple solution to help save lives - a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle... and YOU can help!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>How can I help?</h3>
                    <p>YOU can request vests for your community - and you can make vests and have your friends, business colleagues, church members or club make vests, too!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="view-more-container">
